The paper discusses a privacy-preserving search scheme for encrypted data in cloud-based IoT, which involves topics related to cryptography (cs.CR), databases (cs.DB), information retrieval (cs.IR), cybersecurity (cs.CY), and software engineering (cs.SE). The use of homomorphic encryption and bilinear map also suggests a strong connection to cryptography. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CR, followed by cs.DB, cs.IR, cs.CY, and cs.SE.
